Release-critical bugs status

Fri Oct 2 12:21:00 UTC 2009

for distribution(s): debian

Total number of release-critical bugs: 2103
Number that have a patch: 433
Number that have a fix prepared and waiting to upload: 83
Number that are being ignored: 29
Number concerning the current stable release: 1274
Number concerning the next release: 831

Explanation for bug tags:

  • P: pending
  • +: patch
  • H: help
  • M: moreinfo
  • R: unreproducible
  • S: security
  • U: upstream
  • I: lenny-ignore or squeeze-ignore

The second set of tags indicate what releases a bug applies to: O for oldstable (sarge), S for stable (lenny), T for testing (squeeze), U for unstable (sid) or E for experimental.
